{"tid":1649260,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何慕詩拆穿藍絲謊言","createTime":"2019-10-12T14:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T00:38:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"65b35b0f39f444530cdf3b8a73e0767a7751b041","tid":1649260,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:47:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191012/20785278\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191012%2F20785278&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9oVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=f4017734\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191012%2F20785278&h=8c41bd90\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191012/20785278</a><br />\n<br />\n何慕詩拆穿藍絲謊言<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191012/large/1570801599_97cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191012%2Flarge%2F1570801599_97cb.jpg&h=a23c04a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何慕詩指男士的陰莖裏面沒有骨，認為「骨折」相是P圖。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n現職性治療師的何慕詩，眼見前日藍絲群組瘋傳一張聲稱「警員下體被黃屍暴徒打斷骨」的X光片，當中清楚見到陰莖內出現「骨折」情況，於是前晚在fb開live講解，她表示：「男士嘅陰莖裏面係唔可能有骨，我都有同啲專業人士研究過呢張相，覺得呢張相係有被P圖，就算我哋成日講嘅海綿體，喺X光片裏面亦都係見唔到。」<br />\n<br />\n何慕詩接着詳細分析男士的身體構造，亦解釋在甚麼情況下才會令海綿體受傷，並貼出一張陰莖真的被折斷的相。她說：「其實喺冇勃起嘅情況下，係好難折斷，喺一個暴力鬥爭裏面，受傷嘅朋友喺呢個情況下，陰莖竟然會勃起咗？聽落真係比較荒謬。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：翁可人 <br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：王宗堯參與文宣：無懼白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n王宗堯參與文宣：無懼白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【娛樂人物】蔣雅文蔣雅詩 我們都在公屋長大<br />\n<br />\n王宗堯參與文宣：無懼白色恐怖<br />\n撐中大女生 咒警察落地獄王喜旺角指揮交通"},{"pid":"c73e5ad1fc5da8232932851cfd5f269e7d251a61","tid":1649260,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:06:18.000Z","msg":"狗撚咪有骨<br />\n好make sense"},{"pid":"7d933bef62f7d78f89a568298fadd19ed178ad2f","tid":1649260,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:35:23.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5b461d52af2c2a10c0c0b2ac1b13b4d8b72cf26d","tid":1649260,"uid":299372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}